data.description: This is a Great Home ! Move right In! Possible Seller assist to help make this home your own..  Lots of updates including Updated kitchen and Baths,Heater and central air new in 2020, Beautiful Bamboo flooring on 1st floor,and freshly painted thru out. You will love the open front porch and fenced rear yard/courtyard too.. All 3 bedrooms are good sized with closets and carpeted. The basement is the project you are looking for to turn into a great finished space. Great location close to shopping ,transportation, and 95. Don't Miss this one!
